        "short_description": "Fight alone or with friends in For Honor, a third-person hero-based melee fighting game. Enter the chaos of war as a Knight, a Viking, a Samurai, a Wu Lin, or an Outlander. Fight in brutal PvP and team-oriented modes, or play the thrilling story campaign.",
        "detailed_description": "<h1>YEAR 10 ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/691668bcef1d1e3e5e09ac4ebd90d8a1.avif?t=1778259779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras_big/691668bcef1d1e3e5e09ac4ebd90d8a1.avif?t=1778259779 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Year 10 April Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/82c784191980de3639f07f7905a75fd0.avif?t=1778259779\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></p><br><h1>COMPARISON GRID</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/f51965207c8e4e89b7548afbc8cb2667.avif?t=1778259779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras_big/f51965207c8e4e89b7548afbc8cb2667.avif?t=1778259779 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></p><br><h1>ULTIMATE EDITION</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/b299d4bd517892621d928783e4b74bdb.avif?t=1778259779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras_big/b299d4bd517892621d928783e4b74bdb.avif?t=1778259779 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the Ultimate Edition which includes 12 additional heroes with unique playstyles to get the best experience in For Honor!</p></p><br><h1>GOLD EDITION</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/00ec6e3d173af96e7be69dfe06dfb52d.avif?t=1778259779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras_big/00ec6e3d173af96e7be69dfe06dfb52d.avif?t=1778259779 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the Gold Edition which includes six additional heroes with unique playstyles to upgrade your For Honor experience!</p></p><br><h1>STANDARD EDITION</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/1a876fa559d4f61d2e4d869bc4b0be5e.avif?t=1778259779\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras_big/1a876fa559d4f61d2e4d869bc4b0be5e.avif?t=1778259779 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This pack includes heroes from the standard edition of For Honor.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTER THE ART OF BATTLE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/fd662438a960b1a146c96eb9e1ca2c05.poster.avif?t=1778259779\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/fd662438a960b1a146c96eb9e1ca2c05.webm?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/fd662438a960b1a146c96eb9e1ca2c05.mp4?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Feel the power of every strike with the highly technical Art of Battle control system. Wield your blade according to your style: swift Assassin, tanky Heavy, versatile Vanguard, or technical Hybrid.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A NEVER-ENDING GAME</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/880e3bb84afd2d17093e5964d7e044fc.poster.avif?t=1778259779\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/880e3bb84afd2d17093e5964d7e044fc.webm?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/880e3bb84afd2d17093e5964d7e044fc.mp4?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy an ever-evolving experience with more than 30 heroes, five factions, 18 maps, seasonal events, thousands of gear items, cross-platform play, and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PERSONALIZE YOUR HEROES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/9dd8f2f9a6e7e1b715eae38d3057901d.poster.avif?t=1778259779\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/9dd8f2f9a6e7e1b715eae38d3057901d.webm?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/9dd8f2f9a6e7e1b715eae38d3057901d.mp4?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock rewards and customize your heroes with thousands of different weapons, emblems, and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MEMORABLE STORY CAMPAIGN</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/8f994c2d74639ac525794281a11fa38a.poster.avif?t=1778259779\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/8f994c2d74639ac525794281a11fa38a.webm?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304390/extras/8f994c2d74639ac525794281a11fa38a.mp4?t=1778259779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Storm castles and fortresses in massive battles and confront bosses in intense duels.<br><br><br>Choose the Ultimate Edition to get the best experience, with 12 additional heroes!",
